<h1 style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 400; color: #1a1a1a; margin: 0 0 30px 0;">Password Reset Request</h1>

<p style="font-size: 15px; color: #666; margin: 0 0 25px 0;">
    Dear user <a href="mailto:<%= email %>" style="color: #00a6ff; text-decoration: none;"><%= email %></a>:
</p>

<p style="font-size: 15px; color: #333; line-height: 1.8; margin: 0 0 15px 0;">
    We received a request to reset your password for your CrediScore account. Please use the link below to create a new password as soon as possible.
</p>

<p style="font-size: 15px; color: #333; line-height: 1.8; margin: 25px 0 15px 0;">
    Reset link expires at: <strong style="font-weight: 600;"><%= new Date(Date.now() + 3600000).toLocaleString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: '2-digit', day: '2-digit', hour: '2-digit', minute: '2-digit', second: '2-digit' }) %></strong>
</p>

<p style="font-size: 15px; color: #333; line-height: 1.8; margin: 0 0 15px 0;">
    For more details, please go to <a href="<%= resetUrl %>" style="color: #00a6ff; text-decoration: none;">"Reset Password"</a>.
</p>
